{"tid":961163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到露宿者simon嘅訪問，好多人留言鬧佢係垃圾，冇尊嚴","createTime":"2018-12-30T00:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T16:32:14.000Z","uid":79353,"like":31,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed23f5f43094ba47969a081fc8373853a19edcb","tid":961163,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T00:34:50.000Z","msg":"啲人鬧佢：<br />\n&quot;正垃圾，有手有腳唔搵工返，就算做清潔都係自食其力，好過而家要食二手快餐咁冇尊嚴。你冇盡過供養父母嘅責任，冇貢獻過社會！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後我覺得啲人真係虛偽勢利！就算真係搵到工返，咪又係俾人嫌搵錢少，份工唔夠好聽，成世冇錢途<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有，唔明點解講到返工就好有尊嚴咁。唔通你幫老細維持生意營運，啲錢賺到就入佢袋，你淨係每個月出自己份糧，咁你就好有尊嚴咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2239154/抛卻尊嚴面子過流浪人生%E3%80%80從中產到露宿者：找回人生快樂\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2239154%2F%E6%8A%9B%E5%8D%BB%E5%B0%8A%E5%9A%B4%E9%9D%A2%E5%AD%90%E9%81%8E%E6%B5%81%E6%B5%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%25E3%2580%2580%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%A2%E5%88%B0%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E8%80%85%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%BE%E5%9B%9E%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82&d=Nfsz5E3m9Y1rIgqi3P%2FNwBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9cb62bf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2239154/抛卻尊嚴面子過流浪人生%E3%80%80從中產到露宿者：找回人生快樂</a>"},{"pid":"e80ff23642afae63ba38271bc575f6bd4e9647a4","tid":961163,"uid":16061,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T00:37:30.000Z","msg":"其實佢過得開心咪得 但點解呢排咁多媒體搵佢做訪問吹奏佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e830026db7acd2fd551cb3c3f4e4b37d4910b7","tid":961163,"uid":79353,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e80ff23642afae63ba38271bc575f6bd4e9647a4","tid":961163,"uid":16061,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T00:37:30.000